content: This is just a reminder that you can sign up to phone bank, canvass, get trainings  or take other actions at https://events.democrats.org/ in your state or in one of our battleground states (NC, PA, GA, NH, WI, PA, MI, AZ, NV). Volunteers like you make all the difference! We look forward to seeing you at an event soon.
## [North Dakota Voter Information](https://www.vote.org/state/north-dakota/)

Hello to all of our lovely North Dakota folks! We are looking for someone in ND to host a watch party for the presidential debate on September 10th! If you are interested, please sign up for an info session here: https://events.democrats.org/event/677337/
